                    "title": "Problem Statement",
                    "content": [
                        {
                            "type": "text",
                            "text": "Given an integer array, return the majority element. A majority element is an element that appears more than `n / 2` times. If no such element exists, return `-1`. **Example 1:** ``` Input: [1,2,5,9,5,9,5,5,5] Output: 5 ``` **Example 2:** ``` Input: [3,2] Output: -1 ```"
